description:
Doree and Kate give a pep talk to a listener who wants to improve her confidence, share a follow up email regarding their response to a caller who's unhappy with her boyfriend’s wardrobe, and hear from a newly pregnant listener struggling with her feelings of guilt and anger.

Doree’s on maternity leave, so we’re taking a mini-episode break! There will be no mini-episodes on May 6th, 13th, and 20th. But please keep the voicemails and emails coming: To leave a voicemail for a future episode, call 781-591-0390. You can also email the podcast at forever35podcast@gmail.com.
